Thế anh có thích không?

114
00:05:26,794 --> 00:05:28,827
Ồ, anh thích chứ.

115
00:05:28,829 --> 00:05:31,129
♪ Like a shotgun ♪

116
00:05:31,131 --> 00:05:34,499
♪ I can't be outdone ♪

117
00:05:34,501 --> 00:05:36,702
Whoo!

118
00:05:36,704 --> 00:05:39,104
♪ You gonna get some ♪

119
